snippet.title: Dick Tracy ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
Without doubt one of worst movie licensed games on the ZX Spectrum, it has absolutely nothing!  No gameplay, no lastability, no enjoyment and the best of all, no sound....not even a sqeak!  And all for £10.99!  What more don't you want!

Anyways this game has zippo sound.....hang on I just said that didn't I?  So I've thrown in a little music for "appeal purposes".....and also to make sure you watch this video and live to state how shit it is!

Music taken from the ZX Spectrum version of Crack Down and rehandled and potentially destroyed by me......in otherwords it's in a different pitch from the original....because I can.
